casebody.data:
Dansinger et al., Appellants, v. White, Respondent. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. September 14, 1892.) Action Robert Dansinger and James H. Edward C. White.

Argued before Mayham, P. J., and Putnam and Herrick, JJ.

No opinion. Motion for reargument denied, with costs. For decision on appeal, see 19 N. Y. Supp. 897.
